Cell["\<\
See the notes \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]ScatteringTheoryNotes-NPM-2019.nb\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] for an earlier version of this scattering code with \
the theory background.  See \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]LiPotentials.nb\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] for the background on the hyperfine and Zeeman \
matrix elements and projection operators. Here, I\[CloseCurlyQuote]m copying \
over the relevant modules to have a more compact notebook with only the code, \
and minimal exposition.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.79975054062538*^9, 3.799750601442273*^9}, {
  3.79975110477772*^9, 
